## This action will create ordinals 
## eg the superscript rd in 3rd
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Save the rsb in F1
##
set F1 rsb            
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Do the transformation
##
origin 0 0
stretch 50 50
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Scale rsb
##
set rsb [F1/2]
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Raise the glyph to xheight
##
set ymin xheight
